{
  "_skeleton_name": "zoom-mouvement-30",
  "_description": "Zoom mouvement stock : pattern X.12 a 30 tables, 108 RSQL. Tables canoniques : MOUV, ART, LOTDET, BF, DEPO + lookups.",
